result.name: Kasir Restaurant

reviews.text: The staffs are polite and helpful. The most I like of it is, my relative called the restaurant on my behalf to order some dishes in advance, and a staff ringed me up to verify if its OK to proceed! Great customer service! Food there is generally OK but some of them are salty and oily and make me thirsty. I would suggest the duck with plum sauce & poached shrimps..
This is a hidden jewel in this small town. Highly recommend to call for dishes you would like. Not the best service but some of its dishes are mouth watering.

My family comes here for festive dinners as its fried fish dish （油浸荀殼魚）is done very well. A dish of US oysters with ginger & onions costs HK$188. It is just a place for villagers nearby to park and eat!
Seats are as dirty.

result.formatted_address: 香港藍地青山公路藍地段植園3座
result.name: 嘉爵酒樓

reviews.text: 點心款式太少，一樣點心都要$20-$25，唔太抵死。但呢度D燒味出名很好食，同埋我覺得呢到D炒粉麵飯都幾好味。但比我再選擇的話，我寧願去附近的季季紅好過，因為嗰度點心款式夠多，又好食。
食材份量夠，但價錢不貴，人均消費約$130。服務優良，附設免費停車場。
舊派粵菜，每道菜都做得出色，真才實料，炸生蠔火喉啱啱好，唔失去生蠔嘅鮮味，外表鬆趣，梅菜茄子炒菜心，外面已看不到此等菜色，酸梅鴨（如沒記錯菜名的話😅）入味無比，下面原本陪襯的芋頭比鴨更好味，甘香粉糯，不能錯過，酸梅鴨需提早預訂，但十分籍得，會再來呀👍👍
嘉爵酒樓在藍地，食嘢水準一般， 午餐有老火湯送價錢平，值得一試，有免費泊車。
食品一般，名大於實
